        "evidence": "<p>Addition of the selected points:</p> <div class=\"table-responsive\"> <table class=\"table table-bordered\"> <tbody> <tr> <td>&nbsp;</td> <td> <p><strong>0 points</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>1 point</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>2 points</strong></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><strong>Facial droop</strong></p> </td> <td> <p>Absent</p> </td> <td> <p>Present</p> </td> <td> <p>--</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><strong>Arm drift</strong></p> </td> <td> <p>Absent</p> </td> <td> <p>Drifts down</p> </td> <td> <p>Falls rapidly</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><strong>Grip strength</strong></p> </td> <td> <p>Normal</p> </td> <td> <p>Weak grip</p> </td> <td> <p>No grip</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div>",
        "facts": "<p>Interpretation:</p> <div class=\"table-responsive\"> <table class=\"table table-bordered\"> <tbody> <tr> <td> <p><strong>LAMS</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>Interpretation</strong></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>&lt;4</span></p> </td> <td> <p><span>LVO less likely. Stroke is minor or moderate in severity, but may still benefit from acute treatment.</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>≥4</span></p> </td> <td> <p><span>LVO likely. Stroke is severe and requires acute treatment. Transfer to stroke center with endovascular capabilities.</span></p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <p><span><br>In the </span><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14691787\" target=\"_blank\"><span>derivation study</span></a><span>, lower mean LAMS correlated with lower <calculator id=\"1890\">Modified Rankin Scale score</calculator> (i.e., better functional outcome) at 3 months (mean entry LAMS 2.2 versus 3.7 for mRS ≤1 or &gt;1, respectively).</span></p>",
        "estimation": [],
        "primary_complains": [
